Rafeeq, Qatar’s First 100% Qatari Super App
Rafeeq is Qatar’s only fully Qatari-owned super app. It brings food delivery, groceries, pharmacy items, flowers, gifts, shopping, hotel bookings, and essential services together in one simple experience.
Rafeeq began with food delivery, and it remains our core strength. Today, the app has expanded into major verticals to give you everything you need in one place.

Food delivery is the heart of Rafeeq. Order from Qatar’s top restaurants, including McDonald’s, KFC, Hardee’s, Pizza Hut, Jollibee, Zaatar W Zeit, and many more. From global brands to local favorites, Rafeeq delivers quickly and reliably across the country.

Grocery Delivery Made Easy
Shop your weekly essentials with no queues and no heavy bags. Fresh produce, daily needs, and household items are delivered directly to your door with a simple and fast checkout process.

Pharmacy, Health and Personal Care
Order medicines, skincare, supplements, beauty items, and personal care essentials from trusted pharmacies across Qatar. Enjoy fast, secure, and reliable delivery for all your health needs.

Hotel Booking
Browse and book hotels across Qatar with transparent pricing, an easy booking flow, and instant confirmation. Whether it is a weekend stay, family trip, or business booking, Rafeeq gives you convenient access to top hotels in the country.

Market. Everything You Need in One Place
Explore a wide and growing range of stores across popular shopping categories:
Electronics
Perfumes and beauty
Toys and kids
Accessories
Home and lifestyle


Your favorite stores are now available inside Rafeeq.

Flowers, Gifts and Digital Cards
Send fresh flowers, perfumes, digital cards, or gift cards instantly. Ideal for occasions, celebrations, and last-minute gifts.

Stars. Influencer Stores
Discover exclusive items from your favorite creators inside Rafeeq Stars. This influencer shopping experience is unique and not available in any other app in Qatar.

Essential Services
Book useful services directly through Rafeeq, including:
Home cleaning
Boat trips
Pick and drop services


More lifestyle services are added regularly to make everyday life easier.

Why Choose Rafeeq
The first and only 100 percent Qatari super app
Qatar’s most complete ecosystem for food, shopping, bookings and services
Fast delivery across all areas
Trusted and secure payment options
One app for food, grocery, pharmacy, flowers, gifts, hotels and more


Rafeeq is created in Qatar for the people of Qatar. Convenience, speed and choice in one simple app.

Tired of cooking the same 3 meals on repeat? Zest integrates a mind-blowing cooking education into your routine. Learn to cook with us through step-by-step explanations of foundational cooking concepts in fewer than 10 minutes and dishes that bring the concept to life. Our recipes are created by two former Michelin star chefs, distilled by a home chef, and cooked by you, the superstar home cook that you are (or will be). We don't assume any prior culinary knowledge. We meet you where you are and help you improve.
 
Stop copying traditional recipes - start learning from Zest. We've cooked those delicious Bon Appetit dinners. But when we took away the recipes we felt like lost puppies. Zest is designed to teach you the how's and why's of cooking. So when the recipe is gone you can confidently navigate the kitchen. The promise: Taste improvement after one dinner with Zest.

FEATURES:

STEP-BY-STEP INSTRUCTIONS
We've all tried cooking a TikTok recipe. You rewatch the video 13 times to figure out what the hell is going on. Zest embeds videos throughout recipes so you can click into content when you need it. No more pausing and restarting. Learn at your own pace.
 
CONCEPT VIDEOS
Watch a short video on a new concept at your own pace and then cook recipes that reinforce what you've learned. We dive into topics like the science of tasting and the basics of seasoning, sautéing, roasting and more!

SKILL VIDEOS
Don't know how to dice an onion? Don't be embarrassed, we got you covered. Skill videos are linked in each recipe to guide you along, so you don't have to watch Gordon Ramsey on YouTube (we love his accent too).

CURATED MENU
Choose a menu to fit your preferences. Tired of wasting produce? Search for dishes including what’s already in your fridge. Got allergies? Compile safe recipes in your menu to find them when you’re ready to get cooking. 

GROCERY LIST
Shop your menu with our automated grocery list. Plus, utilize our helpful tips while you shop. Don't know what a neutral oil is? We got you covered.

PERSONALIZED RECOMMENDATIONS
Rate the recipes you cook, so we can recommend similar ones.

Feedback? Technical Issues? Killer ideas you want to contribute to make our app better? Email us at support@zestapp.co. We're always here to help and would love to chef up new ideas together!

Happy ordering.
